      "message": "save() saves entities in one multiPut, I don\u0027t know what else to write as a comment, but it would not clarify your 2nd question anyway. Suggestions for what would be useful?\n\nAs for 2nd question:\nneither load() nor save() deal with transaction retries, they do exact the same work regardless of first or n-th try. This is how datastore.RunInTransaction(ctx, func, retryPolicy) works: if func fails, the whole func may be retried.",
